---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Phill | AI Search Optimization Expert" 
  description="About Phill — Specialist in AI SEO and Answer Engine Optimization (AEO). Structuring web data so your business is recommended by conversational search models."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-20">
    
    <header class="mb-12 pt-10" transition:animate="fade">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center md:items-start">
        <img 
          src="/images/phill.jpg" 
          alt="Phill Savage — Generative Search Architect" 
          class="w-40 h-40 rounded-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 border-4 border-white dark:border-slate-800 shadow-xl flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4 font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
            I make sure AI models <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">recommend your business.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
            Ten years managing web infrastructure. Now structuring site data so your business wins the AI search era.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 py-6 mb-12 border-y border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60" transition:animate="fade">
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10+</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Years Experience</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">100+</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Brands Managed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1 text-center md:text-left">
        <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Ace MS</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Agency Leadership</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mb-16 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300" transition:animate="fade">
      <p>
        I’ve spent the last decade leading technical web projects from the ground up. Most of that time has been spent running operations as a director at <strong><a href="https://acemsthailand.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300">Ace Marketing Solutions</a></strong>. 
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Under that same banner, I serve as the Project Director for the <strong><a href="https://offsitethailand.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400 dark:hover:text-blue-300" target="_blank">Offsite Thailand</a></strong> program, coordinating ground logistics, local venues, and end-to-end retreat operations for remote-first software companies.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Over my career, I’ve directly managed the digital setups and platform strategies for <strong>over 100 brands</strong>, ranging from regional boutique hotels to Fortune 500 enterprises.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">The Shift to AI Search</h2>
      <p>
        The web is shifting completely. Active buyers are moving away from browsing standard lists of blue links on Google, turning instead to conversational summaries on platforms like ChatGPT, Gemini, and Perplexity. If your online content isn't built to answer their direct questions, your company simply disappears from their recommendations.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        That’s why I focus strictly on <strong>Generative Search Architecture</strong>. I don't deal in surface-level marketing fluff. I optimize the foundational information layers of your website so AI search models easily find, trust, and reference your business.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-16" transition:animate="fade">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Technical Focus Areas</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">AI Search Diagnostics</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Fixing the broken public data that causes ChatGPT, Perplexity, or Gemini to hallucinate your pricing, list wrong contact info, or actively recommend your competitors instead of you.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">AI Recommendation Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Structuring your website data so when buyers ask an AI engine for the "best B2B platform" or "top regional service," your business is consistently pushed forward as the primary choice.
          </p>
        </div>
      
        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60 md:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Speed & Security Upgrades (Astro Migration)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Ditching slow, heavy database platforms for streamlined flat-file code. This eliminates your server hack risks entirely, cuts hosting costs, and makes your site lightning-fast for both human visitors and AI data crawlers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-left" transition:animate="fade">
      <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        When I’m not analyzing AI visibility footprints or engineering site architectures, I’m usually developing clean web systems or publishing my findings in my <a href="/journal" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 underline hover:no-underline">journal</a>.
      </p>
      
      <a 
        href="mailto:hello@psavage.net?subject=Consulting%20Inquiry%20—%20Generative%20Search" 
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition-colors bg-blue-600 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-100"
      >
        Let's talk strategy
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>